
echo: User container to echo back user input

To run (load and start) container:

$ mwtest.py -c100 run echo.img

To send data to the echo container:

$ cmtest cmd -f100 "Hello World"
Sending data to CMRT via SIC...
...received 20 bytes OK
00000000: 01 00 00 00 0b 00 00 00  48 65 6c 6c 6f 20 57 6f  |........Hello Wo|
00000010: 72 6c 64 00                                       |rld.|

To unload container:

$ mwtest.py -c100 unload
